Ing '''Shard London Bridge''' o '''The Shard''' (a sadya dang awsang '''London Bridge Tower'''<ref>[http://www.designbuild-network.com/projects/london-bridge/ London Bridge Tower, London]. Design Build Network. Retrieved 7 July 2010.</ref><ref>{{cite news |url= http://www.worldarchitecturenews.com/index.php?fuseaction=wanappln.projectview&upload_id=1387  |work=World Architecture News |accessdate =7 July 2010 |date= 10 September 2007 |title= Shard funding crisis: Tower finances cast shadow over project}}</ref> o '''Shard of Glass''')<ref>{{cite news |url= http://www.thisislondon.co.uk/standard/article-23651085-28bn-shard-of-glass-to-start-its-ascent.do |title= £28bn Shard of Glass to start its ascent |newspaper=London Evening Standard |date= 24 February 2009 |accessdate =7 July 2010 |first= Mira |last= Bar-Hillel}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url= http://www.nce.co.uk/news/structures/work-starts-on-shard-of-glass/1996445.article |title= Work starts on Shard of Glass |work=New Civil Engineer |date=2 April 2009 |accessdate=7 July 2010}}</ref> metung yang [[skyscraper]] king [[Southwark]], London. Maki katas yang  {{convert|309.6|m|ft}} babo ning gabun, at yang [[Listahan da reng pekamatas a gusali king   Europa|pekamatas a gusali king Europa]] anyang Julio 2012. Iti murin ing kadang pekamatas a istruktura [[Listahan da reng pekamatas a istruktura king United Kingdom|king in United Kingdom]], katuki ning {{convert|330|m|ft|0|adj=on}} toreng kongkretu king [[Emley Moor transmitting station]].

Elilan ne ning The Shard ing [[Southwark Towers]], metung a 24-pisu o palapag a gusaling pang-upisina king katatalakaran na a mitikdo anyang 1975. I [[Renzo Piano]], ing arkitektu ning the Shard's architect, megobra ya king kumpanyang pang inhenyeria (''engineering firm'') a ing   [[Broadway Malyan]] anyang panaun ning pamagplanu. Atin yang 72 pisu o palapag a malyaring gamitan ing tori, ampong viewing gallery at makabuklat a observation deck – ing pekamatas king UK  – king ka-72ng pisu, king katas a {{convert|245|m|ft}}.<ref>[http://www.cnplus.co.uk/technical/tall-buildings/shard-observation-deck-to-be-europes-highest/5202330.article "Shard observation deck to be Europe's highest"]. CNPlus.co.uk, 20 May 2009. Retrieved 2 February 2012.</ref> Midisenyu ya ing The Shard king tabas o ubug a irregular a [[Pyramid (geometry)|pramide]] (''pyramid'') manibat king pundasyun angga king babo, at laganas yang mibabalut king salamin. Miyari ya ing kayang istruktura anyang Abril 2012, at mibuklat ya king publiku anyang 5 Julio 2012.<ref>[http://www.london-se1.co.uk/news/view/5976 "Prince Andrew and Qatari prime minister to open Shard on 5 July"]. LondonSE1, 30 April 2012. Retrieved 1 May 2012.</ref><ref name=GulfTi2012>[http://www.gulf-times.com/site/topics/article.asp?cu_no=2&item_no=478894&version=1&template_id=57&parent_id=56 "Qatar's Shard the tallest building in Europe now"]. ''Gulf Times'', 3 January 2012. Retrieved 6 January 2012.</ref>

